abstract: Kevin Kisner takes first round lead at RSM Classic golf tournament; other golf news noted.
lead_paragraph: Kisner made an eagle on his penultimate hole for a seven-under-par 65 on the Plantation Course, giving him a one-shot lead relative to par after the first round of the RSM Classic.

headline.main: Kevin Kisner Takes Lead in Georgia With a Seven-Under 65
